<arggraph id="micro_c087" topic_id="video_games_as_teaching_tools" stance="con">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Schools should not use video games as a teaching tool.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[Videogames hurt the eyes of children]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[and can be violent.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[They will view school time as entertainment and not as serious.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[They will not learn as much]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[and will not succeed because of these video games.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[Some might say that video games will get the attention of these students,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[but I think that this opinion is a myth and is not based in fact.]]></edu>
